&gt; Melchana focused her optics and saw vaguely the feline form in the
&gt; dark. Then she started laughing out loud.
&gt; 
&gt; Melchana: Autobots? Decepticons? Quintesson expirement? Oh boy! You
&gt; are funny! Me and all the new rulers of this planet have nothing to do
&gt; with any of those!

She growled sourly. Was this one making fun of her?! 

&gt; 
&gt; She walked a little closer, but still at a good range.
&gt; 
&gt; Melchana: I&#39;m Melchana. A Tripredacus. I&#39;m not organic, even partly,
&gt; but my body is composed of nanites that imitate organic matter... only
&gt; better. As for you... we detected you and we wanted to see what you
&gt; were. What are you?
&gt; 
&gt; 
Staying in the shadow, imitating Ravage. After spending her many years near 
him, as well as other Decepticon comrades, she had picked up components of 
their personality & actions. 

Hesitating a moment. &quot;I am Maxima. A Decepticon. Or.. was.&quot; Her feline form 
of white & black stripes shifted in the shadows. &quot;I have no idea who did this 
to me. But rest assured, I WILL make them prize scrap metal presents for the 
Junkions!&quot; 

&quot;This is shameful to be in this form.&quot; pausing. &quot;You mentioned you are a... 
Tripredacus. I am not familiar with that term.&quot; she was calm now, curious as 
to what was going on. Maybe this one who confronted her would know what is 
going on. & she would bend this to her advantage. &quot;I know I am still on 
Cybertron. I do hope. Last I remember, was a battle. I was heavily damaged. I 
& a couple Decepticons fleed to the lower depths in hopes to get to Vector 
Sigma, but never reached the Vector Sigma chamber. I hid & went into Stasis 
Lock in the Decepticon crypt. Then recently.. I was restored to normal 
functioning perameters, but not in m form, but this horrific trans-organic 
form.&quot; 

She watched her &#39;guest&#39; intently.  

